{"tid":1276263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搵外國片商，將反送中拍成電影","createTime":"2019-07-02T02:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T13:32:47.000Z","uid":259907,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"81ecf5adfa10af59b579593f7d3ea40a8eeb4d3a","tid":1276263,"uid":259907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"有個idea可以將香港人今次呢種精神延續落去，就係搵外國片商，將成件事反送中為題材，拍成電影。<br />\n<br />\n我諗到嘅有孤星淚嘅導演Tom Hooper. 有無人有建議？搵外國人拍，係因為西片先可以打入全球市場。"},{"pid":"6969aa53bb5cfb00b164bb224a2889f12b43d201","tid":1276263,"uid":259907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"但材料我地都需要準備好，包括：<br />\n<br />\n各事嘅時序<br />\n感情位<br />\n團結因素<br />\n香港核心<br />\n各立場及戰場位置"},{"pid":"61fca17bf93090c78f7fab71610359251782dab6","tid":1276263,"uid":256205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6969aa53bb5cfb00b164bb224a2889f12b43d201","tid":1276263,"uid":259907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"但材料我地都需要準備好，包括：<br />\n<br />\n各事嘅時序<br />\n感情位<br />\n團結因素<br />\n香港核心<br />\n各立場及戰場位置"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"錄音機"},{"pid":"6ff3828269d438302c222290384988b9b818741d","tid":1276263,"uid":259907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"即係我地要將事實document 咗佢先"},{"pid":"e08ddc1dc38d436282921eb7cc824c0b364ae2c5","tid":1276263,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但材料我地都需要準備好，包括：<br />\n<br />\n各事嘅時序<br />\n感情位<br />\n團結因素<br />\n香港核心<br />\n各立場及戰場位置</blockquote>器材：錄音機<br />\n歡迎補充</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e1752d6a281bae79a82a42e4c5545af076ba8c28","tid":1276263,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276407fd3dfff4c0eb09a55e07519b5166b91f44","tid":1276263,"uid":52238,"like